title: The key things you must give up to lose weight

description:

So many of us focus on the food we need to give up in order to lose weight. Today I talk about what we really need to give up: regret, our past, fear of failure, and other stories we tell ourselves to NOT do the basics of weightloss. Hold on. It's a PREACH day.
